abstract: Estimate of self-assessed health as fair or poor health from the Australian Health Survey, from 2011 to 2013, by SA2. SA2 data for this indicator are derived from Population Health Area (PHA) data. PHAs are comprised of one or more whole SA2s. A full listing of SA2s and what percentage of their corresponding PHA has been allocated to them can be found at the following link: http://publichealth.gov.au/AURIN/phidu_PHA_to_SA2_concordance.xls
